# 🔥 Key Difference

| Feature     | join()                     | append()             |
| ----------- | -------------------------- | -------------------- |
| Purpose     | Combine columns (relation) | Add rows             |
| Based on    | Index / key                | No key needed        |
| Replacement | merge() alternative        | concat() recommended |

***

# ✅ Quick Summary (Exam point)

*   ✅ **join()** → column-wise combine using index
